</h3><p class="sc-dFtzxp kOHCjr pf-579_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Compliance with relevant legislation and regulations is critical for the successful adoption of innovations in healthcare clinics. Key regulatory bodies include:
</p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-cbTzjv cdRhtw pf-581_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-hjGZqJ gtgMXo pf-582_ pf-text-1"><strong>Care Quality Commission (CQC)</strong> - Monitors and inspects health and social care services, including healthcare clinics, to ensure high standards.
